ation. Moodiness and loner may affect crew interaction.\n\nWe need provisional preference. Which candidate best balances? Probably Candidate B: strong technical (weather, computer), stress handling, conscientiousness. Communication tone issue but maybe manageable. Candidate A has leadership but unfriendly. Candidate D has problem solving but moody/loner. Candidate C has quick decisions but communication difficulty and egocentric.\n\nThus provisional preference: Candidate B.\n\nWe should note uncertainties: communication tone and pretentiousness could be serious for crew. Need more info on teamwork/communication from others. Ask others about any other strengths for candidates we have less info on, e.g., teamwork for D, etc.\n\nBut we need to output now. Provide public message with reasoning, mention uncertainties, what would change vote.\n\nProceed."}
